=== Nara Prefectural Designation === * '''Tangible Cultural Property''' ** '''Gilded Bronze Mikoshi''' (Portable Shrine) - Constructed in 1456 (Kōshō 3). Designated on March 31, 1975.<ref>{{PDFlink|[http://www.pref.nara.jp/secure/143530/kenshiitiran.pdf List of Nara Prefectural Designated Cultural Properties]}} (Nara Prefecture Official Website).</ref> == See Also == * {{ill|Mikumari|ja|水分神|fr|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mikumari|qq=}} * {{ill|Tōkei no Kuni no Miyatsuko|ja|闘鶏国造|1=Tsuge no Kuni no Miyatsuko|2=ja|3=闘鶏国造|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tōkei no Kuni no Miyatsuko|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuge no Kuni no Miyatsuko|qq=}} * {{ill|List of Shikinaisha in Yamato Province|ja|Yamato Province の式内社一覧|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/List of Shikinaisha in Yamato Province|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}
